 《超人》剧组成员在亚特兰大片场附近被发现死亡https://www.nme.com/news/film/member-of-superman-crew-found-dead-near-atlanta-set-3778140?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=member-of-superman-crew-found-亚特兰大附近死亡集Emma WilkesThu, 25 Jul 2024 21:07:27 +0000 Film NewsNews.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3778140 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>死亡事件未被视为可疑或与当前项目无关</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/member-of-superman-crew-found-dead-near-atlanta-set-3778140">《超人》剧组成员在亚特兰大片场附近被发现死亡的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一名在华纳兄弟片场工作的工作人员。周三（7 月 24 日），<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/superman"><em>超人</em></a>电影在亚特兰大附近拍摄时被发现死于自杀。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/superman-crewmember-apparent-suicide-atlanta-set-1235957959/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》</em></a>报道，当天清晨，费耶特维尔警察局的警官和护理人员被叫到电影制片厂后，在她的车里发现了这名女剧组成员的尸体。</p><p>费耶特维尔警官在一份声明中写道：“收集的证据表明没有谋杀嫌疑，调查也与任何正在进行的工作室项目无关。”</p><p>该媒体表示，无法联系到华纳兄弟 DC 漫画的代表直接置评。</p><p>这部即将上映的电影最初被命名为<em>《超人</em><em>：遗产》，现在简单地命名为《超人》</em> ，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/who-is-the-new-superman-david-corenswet-3462605">大卫·科伦斯韦特</a>担任同名角色。这部电影预计于 2025 年 7 月上映，标志着<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/dc-extended-universe">DC 宇宙</a>新版本的推出。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6ogjVERTl8/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869